QuestData.Title: The Soulhunter
QuestData.Description: Imonar is the deadliest bounty hunter the Twisting Nether has ever produced. Find a pit to throw him down.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat Imonar the Soulhunter in Antorus, the Burning Throne.

Objectives.Objective: Defeat Imonar the Soul Hunter in the Antorus, The Burning Throne
